{"tid":355591,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)巴斯光年 反斗奇兵1-3","createTime":"2017-08-11T11:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T17:25:19.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43e8db9be5d338a73b68876ccf0f59c596c621e4","tid":355591,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=94e34b65\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=02dc06fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有dailymotion<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6fe71d61\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.travelliker.com.hk/img/upload/img/6-65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.travelliker.com.hk%2Fimg%2Fupload%2Fimg%2F6-65.jpg&h=d811efd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/008-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2F008-2.jpg&h=ccbb5ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/001-95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2F001-95.jpg&h=5b9918a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.巴斯光年是星際總部裡捍衛宇宙的太空騎警，在一次任務失去最佳搭檔後，發誓從此都要單獨執行任務。就在此時，邪惡的札克天王竟利用神秘的力量改造星際總部成員的心智，準備奪取宇宙的控制權。為了維護宇宙和平，巴斯光年勇敢獨自迎戰頭號敵人，沒想到竟在緊要關頭落入敵手！身處險境的巴斯光年，會願意接受新搭檔美娜洛..<br />\n<br />\n2.傳統牛仔玩偶「胡迪」（Woody）是小主人安弟（Andy）最喜歡的玩具，可是熱門玩具「巴斯光年」來了之後讓胡迪失寵。胡迪為了要趕走巴斯卻反被其他玩具們唾棄，之後意外與巴斯一起陷入致命危機，兩個冤家的冒險之旅也由此展開。巴斯光年原本深信自己是要拯救地球的太空騎警，但他後來卻發現自己只是個玩具遂陷入沮喪。當巴斯萬念俱灰，胡迪則設法要逃出玩具虐待狂阿薛的家..<br />\n<br />\n3.在《玩具總動員》之後的某天，主人安迪準備帶胡迪到牛仔俱樂部玩，但不慎將胡迪的胳膊縫線弄斷了，這讓胡迪十分憂鬱，擔心主人會將自己拋棄。不久，安迪的媽媽在家進行大掃除時準備將舊企鵝Wheezy扔掉，胡迪決定從院子把Wheezy拯救回來。當胡迪騎著小狗Buster將Wheezy救回時，自己卻被遺留在院子裡。玩具商艾耳在院子發現了胡迪，經交涉後由於無法獲得胡迪這個絕版玩具，艾耳偷走胡迪，把他帶到了他自己的玩具工廠。巴斯光年嘗試從艾耳手中拯救胡迪卻未能成功，但是玩具們獲悉胡迪就在艾耳的玩具工廠後，巴斯和彈簧狗、番薯頭先生、恐龍及豬仔錢罐火腿開始了拯救胡迪的任務......<br />\n<br />\n4.自從十一年前玩具們所經歷的大冒險後，玩具們安然無恙的度過了好幾個年頭。轉眼間，玩具們的主人安弟已經成為一個青少年，也即將離家去展開他的大學生涯。胡迪與巴斯以及其他的玩具們也都人心惶惶，深怕這個他們內心最恐懼被丟棄的一天即將來臨。這一天，安弟的媽媽來到安弟的房間，詢問他將如何處置這些伴他渡過童年的玩具們，並且要求安弟在離家前要把這些東西處理好，如果沒有將要留下的玩具放置閣樓收藏，她就會把這些玩具處理掉。安弟在媽媽的逼迫下，再次打開他的玩具箱，童年回憶湧上心頭...<br />\n<br />\n8 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=71320669\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c70b7cd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33aac5ea6b347266f0ccfa8d452dc8e71767a36b","tid":355591,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55745ccebd26325b03f51be022bac1319742ec8e","tid":355591,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a832b3c64d8ed0a4d03ee0d026deea33fb96a19d","tid":355591,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e01a8a5652eb0f631527f4ddd5aa444d579db4","tid":355591,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cc9aa30da3c625b897a99428f756057eec3329","tid":355591,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf55eb1f8e2a1d182b5f94c2c590392d9768772","tid":355591,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200d7b71f6b63f62eea95ad23